        "arabicnumber": 1523,
        "text": "Narrated Umm Salamah:That the Prophet (ﷺ) said: \"Whoever sees the crescent of Dhul-Hijjah, and wants to slaughter a sacrifice he should not take from his hair nor from his nails",
        "grades": [
